homeText: Our complex is a futuristic comfort-class complex with modern planning, high quality construction and well-developed infrastructure in the heart of Kyiv. It is designed not only to meet all your requirements for the quality of housing, but also to meet new technologies of comfort!
aboutMain: Our complex is a futuristic comfort-class complex with modern planning, high quality construction and well-developed infrastructure in the heart of Kyiv. It is designed not only to meet all your requirements for the quality of housing, but also to meet new technologies of comfort!
firstCardText: Our complex is just a 5-minute walk from the Golden Gate metro station.
secondCardText: We offer the most modern apartments and rooms for your comfort. Everything related to our facilities is high-tech and new.
thirdCardText: Also, after buying an apartment or commercial space, you will be able to buy a place in a large and convenient underground parking lot a minute from the complex.
